OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting fine and dry with
OL,6,Flittle cloud and light winds. By the
OL,7,Fafternoon some patchy cloud will
OL,8,Fdevelop, and there is a low risk of
OL,9,Fisolated thunderstorms in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry, with cloud building
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and brisk
OL,14,Fnortheasterly winds developing. Some
OL,15,Flow cloud may spread in from the coast
OL,16,Flater overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
