OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fdissipating to leave a generally dry
OL,7,Fday. A small risk of isolated showers
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Feeling slightly
OL,9,Fcooler in the brisk easterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FMostly dry, with temperatures starting
OL,13,Fto increase again from Thursday.
OL,14,FShowers possible Thursday evening and
OL,15,Fearly on Friday. Cloudy but dry on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
